fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 1+2+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, AA, 0, 1, AA, BB, 1, 0, BB, 1, 0, 0, -1

del 1 return
"symbolic2D": add2 -a/2, -b pen gs_symbol_pen if iCooktopSymbolType = 3 or iCooktopSymbolType = 4 then aorb=a if (a-b) > EPS then aorb = b endif if iCooktopSymbolType = 1 then line2 a, 0, 2/5*a, b/2 line2 2/5*a, b/2, 3/5*a, b/2 line2 3/5*a, b/2, 0, b endif if iCooktopSymbolType = 2 then add2 a/2, b/2 line2 -a/5, -b/3.5, a/5, -b/3.5 line2 -a/5, 0, a/10, 0 line2 -a/5, b/3.5, -a/5, -b/3.5 line2 -a/5, b/3.5, a/5, b/3.5 del 1 endif if iCooktopSymbolType = 3 then add2 a/2, b/2 line2 -a/2, b/4, a/2, b/4 add2 0, -b/10 gosub "circle" del 2 endif if iCooktopSymbolType = 4 then add2 a/2, b/2 add2 -a/4, -b/4 gosub "circle" del 1 add2 0, b/4 gosub "circle" del 1 add2 a/4, -b/4 gosub "circle" del 1 del 1 endif del 1 return
"circle": circle2 0, 0, aorb/10 fill gs_symbol_fill_type poly2_b 7, 1+2+64, gs_symbol_pen, gs_back_pen, aorb/10, 0, 1, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180, 4001, -aorb/10, 0, 1, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180, 4001, aorb/10, 0, 1
return
